      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·014.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">何草不黃.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>何草不黃？何日不行？何人不將？經營四方。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Every plant is yellow;
Every day we march.
Every man is moving about,
Doing service in some quarter of the kingdom.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-yuzao-014__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
