      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·014.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">何草不黃.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>何草不玄？何人不矜？哀我征夫，獨為匪民。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Every plant is purple;
Every man is torn from his wife.
Alas for us employed on these expeditions!
How are we alone dealt with as if we were not men?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
