      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·014.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">何草不黃.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>匪兕匪虎，率彼曠野。哀我征夫，朝夕不暇。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>We are not rhinoceroses, we are not tigers,
To be kept in these desolate wilds.
Alas for us employed on these expeditions!
Morning and night we have no leisure.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
