      <prop type="x-translation-ref">何草不黃.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>有芃者狐，率彼幽草。有棧之車，行彼周道。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The long-tailed foxes,
May keep among the dark grass.
And our box-carts,
Keep moving along the great roads.</seg>
      </tuv>
